    "raw_ingredients": "Kleurcrème / Crème Colorante: Aqua / Water Cetearyl Alcohol, Propylene Glycol, Deceth-3, Laureth-12, Ethanolamine,Oleth-30 , Lauric Acid ,Polyquaternium-6, Toluene-2,5-diamine, Glycol Distearate, Sodium Metasilicate, Hexadimethrine Chloride,  Silica Dimethyl Silylate [Nano] / Silica Dimethyl Silylate,Resorcinol, Ci 77491 / Iron Oxides, Ci 77891 / Titanium Dioxide, M-aminophenol, Ascorbic Acid, Mica, Thiolactic Acid,  Thioglycerin, 2-methylresorcinol, N,n-bis(2-hydroxyethyl)-p-phenylenediamine Sulfate,  Carbomer,  Edta, Tetrasodium Edta, 2,4-diaminophenoxyethanol Hcl, Parfum / Fragrance. (F.I.L. Z295115/1).",
